---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="5 分钟快速安装 OpenClaw - 龙虾助理">
  <h1>📥 5 分钟快速安装 OpenClaw</h1>
  <p class="tag">新手入门 第 2 篇</p>

  <div class="tip">
    <p><strong>一句话总结：</strong>选择你的操作系统，跟着步骤走，10 分钟搞定！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="toc">
    <h3>📑 目录</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#windows">🪟 Windows 安装指南</a></li>
      <li><a href="#macos">🍎 macOS 安装指南</a></li>
      <li><a href="#linux">🐧 Linux 安装指南</a></li>
      <li><a href="#api-key">配置 API Key</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faq">常见问题</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="windows">🪟 Windows 安装指南</h2>

  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Windows 10/11</li>
    <li>Node.js 18+ (<a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank">下载地址</a>)</li>
    <li>PowerShell 或 CMD</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>访问 <a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank">https://nodejs.org/</a></li>
      <li>下载 LTS 版本（推荐 20.x）</li>
      <li>运行安装程序，一路 Next</li>
      <li>验证安装：
        <pre><code>node --version
npm --version</code></pre>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <p>以管理员身份打开 PowerShell，运行：</p>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">3</span>
    <h3>初始化工作区</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>mkdir my-assistant
cd my-assistant
openclaw init</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">4</span>
    <h3>启动 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>openclaw start</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="macos">🍎 macOS 安装指南</h2>

  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>macOS 10.15+</li>
    <li>Node.js 18+ (推荐用 Homebrew 安装)</li>
    <li>Terminal</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Homebrew（如果没有）</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>brew install node</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">3</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="linux">🐧 Linux 安装指南</h2>

  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Ubuntu 20.04+ / Debian 11+ / CentOS 8+</li>
    <li>Node.js 18+</li>
    <li>sudo 权限</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    
    <h4>Ubuntu/Debian:</h4>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs</code></pre>

    <h4>CentOS/RHEL:</h4>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>curl -fsSL https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | sudo bash -
sudo yum install -y nodejs</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>sudo npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="api-key">配置 API Key（所有系统通用）</h2>

  <div class="tip warning">
    <p>⚠️ <strong>重要：</strong>OpenClaw 需要配置大模型 API 才能工作</p>
  </div>

  <ol>
    <li>访问阿里云百炼控制台 (<a href="https://bailian.console.aliyun.com/" target="_blank">链接</a>)</li>
    <li>注册/登录账号</li>
    <li>创建 API Key</li>
    <li>复制 Key 到配置文件</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>配置文件位置</h3>
  <div class="code-compare">
    <div>
      <strong>Windows:</strong>
      <pre><code>%APPDATA%\openclaw\config.json</code></pre>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Mac/Linux:</strong>
      <pre><code>~/.openclaw/config.json</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>配置示例</h3>
  <pre class="language-json"><code>{
  "defaultModel": "bailian/qwen3.5-plus",
  "apiKey": "你的 API_KEY"
}</code></pre>

  <h2 id="verify">验证安装</h2>

  <pre class="language-bash"><code>openclaw --version
openclaw status
openclaw ask "你好，请介绍一下自己"</code></pre>

  <h2 id="faq">常见问题</h2>

  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ 安装失败怎么办？</h3>
    <p>清理 npm 缓存后重试：</p>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>npm cache clean --force
npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ 找不到 openclaw 命令？</h3>
    <p>检查 npm 全局路径是否在系统 PATH 中：</p>
    <pre class="language-bash"><code>npm config get prefix</code></pre>
    <p>将返回的路径添加到系统环境变量 PATH</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ API Key 无效？</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>检查 Key 是否正确复制（无多余空格）</li>
      <li>确认账号有足够额度</li>
      <li>检查模型名称是否正确</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="feedback-section">
    <h3>📝 这篇文章有帮助吗？</h3>
    <div class="feedback-buttons">
      <button class="feedback-btn" data-feedback="yes">👍 有用</button>
      <button class="feedback-btn" data-feedback="no">👎 无用</button>
    </div>
    <p class="feedback-note">你的反馈帮助我们改进内容</p>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/guide/" class="btn btn-secondary">← 上一步：OpenClaw 是什么</a>
    <a href="/guide/first-chat/" class="btn">下一步：第一次对话 →</a>
  </div>

  <style>
    .toc {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
    }
    
    .toc h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .toc ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    }
    
    .toc li {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    
    .toc a {
      color: #374151;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .toc a:hover {
      color: #dc2626;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .step {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 4rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 2.5rem;
      height: 2.5rem;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .step h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    .tip {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }
    
    .tip.warning {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    }
    
    .code-compare {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    
    .code-compare div {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .faq {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
    }
    
    .faq h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #0369a1;
    }
    
    .feedback-section {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
    }
    
    .feedback-section h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    .feedback-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    
    .feedback-btn {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    
    .feedback-btn:hover {
      border-color: #dc2626;
      background: #fef2f2;
    }
    
    .feedback-note {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .nav-buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background: #b91c1c;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #4b5563;
    }
    
    pre {
      background: #1f2937;
      color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    
    code {
      font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    
    hr {
      margin: 3rem 0;
      border: none;
      border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    // 反馈功能
    document.querySelectorAll('.feedback-btn').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const feedback = btn.dataset.feedback;
        const section = btn.closest('.feedback-section');
        
        if (feedback === 'yes') {
          section.innerHTML = '<p style="color: #16a34a; font-size: 1.25rem;">✅ 感谢你的反馈！</p>';
        } else {
          section.innerHTML = '<p style="color: #dc2626; font-size: 1.25rem;">💬 请告诉我们如何改进：contact@longxiazhuli.com</p>';
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
